-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">P II</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">X</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">X</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top" /><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top" /></tr><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">strykes fra Schedule IV</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top" /><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top" /><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top" /><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top" /></tr></tbody></table></article> <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">Under fotnote 2 gjøres følgende endring:</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/" id="ledd-2">Tillatelse til å foreskrive sentralstimulerende midler gis av Statens legemiddelkontroll.</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/" id="ledd-3">Endringene trer i kraft straks.</article></main></body></html>